'''''Carbon Balance and Management''''' is a [[Peer review|peer-reviewed]] [[Open access (publishing)|open-access]] [[scientific journal]] published by [[BioMed Central]]. The journal covers research on the global [[carbon cycle]].<ref>{{Cite journal | last1 = Dickinson | first1 = R. | journal = Carbon Balance and Management | volume = 1 | pages = 1 |title=Welcome to ''Carbon Balance and Management''| year = 2006 | doi = 10.1186/1750-0680-1-1}}</ref> The journal was established in 2006 and is abstracted and indexed in [[PubMed]], [[Agricola (database)|Agricola]], [[CAB International]], [[Chemical Abstracts Service]], [[EMBASE]], and [[Scopus]].

